\ls2\ilvl1
\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}Made every Sparkle class private except for SUUpdater, SUAppcast, SUAppcastItem, and the SUVersionComparisonProtocol.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}There is now a single SUUpdater singleton for every host bundle; instead of -[SUUpdater setHostBundle], you can use +[SUUpdater updaterForBundle].\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}Redefined the (entire) delegate protocol accordingly.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}Renamed -[SUUpdater updatePreferencesChanged] to -[SUUpdater resetUpdateCycle]. This provides better semantics for non-apps, which need to start the update cycle manually.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}-[SUUpdater checkForUpdatesWithDriver] is private. If you were using SUProbingUpdateDriver, you can now use -[SUUpdater checkForUpdateInformation] for a similar effect.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}All the user defaults keys are now private; instead, SUUpdater is KVC-compliant for automaticallyChecksForUpdates, updateCheckInterval, and feedURL.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\ql\qnatural\pardirnatural
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}Reduced the size of the English-only framework by 25%.\
{\listtext	\'95	}System profiling information is now only submitted to the server once per week; this will help normalize your statistics across users with different interval preferences.\
{\listtext	\'95	}The feedParamatersForUpdater: delegate method now requires "displayKey" and "displayVersion" keys so that it can inform the user what's being sent.\
{\listtext	\'95	}Added a delegate method called pathToRelaunchForUpdater: which can be used for plugins to provide the path which should be used when relaunching the client after installing an update.\
{\listtext	\'95	}Added support for xml:lang to pick localized nodes in appcasts (for release notes, etc).\
{\listtext	\'95	}Fixed a bug which would cause the "checking for updates" window to not disappear in certain extraordinary error conditions.\
{\listtext	\'95	}Fixed a DSA signature checking bug for .tar.gz archives.\
{\listtext	\'95	}Sparkle now refuses to update on any read-only volume, not just dmgs.\
{\listtext	\'95	}Sparkle will clean up the host app's name and version before sending it as the user agent string; some non-ASCII characters were causing problems.\
{\listtext	\'95	}Added an Italian localization courtesy Michele Longhi.\
{\listtext	\'95	}Added a Swedish localization courtesy Daniel Bergman.\
{\listtext	\'95	}Fixes to the French localization courtesy Ronald Leroux and Yann Ricqueberg.\
{\listtext	\'95	}Fixes to the German localization courtesy Sven-S. Porst.\
{\listtext	\'95	}Fixes to the Russian localization courtesy Alexander Bykov and Anton Sotkov.\
{\listtext	\'95	}Fixed a number of issues related to archive format detection: I reverted back to extensions from UTIs.\
{\listtext	\'95	}Focus behavior fixes for LSUIElement apps.\
{\listtext	\'95	}The status window progress bar now animates even when indeterminate.\
{\listtext	\'95	}Major refactorings to improve functionality for non-app bundles.\
